Usage: group_path [-help] [-comment <string>] -name <path_group_name> [ [-from <from_list>] [-to <to_list>] [-through <through_list>] ]

-help                       # Prints out the command usage
-comment <string>           # Not supported option (string, optional)
-from <from_list>           # List of pins, instances, or clocks that are the
                            # start of the paths (string, optional)
-name <path_group_name>     # The name of the path group (string, required)
-through <through_list>     # List of pins or instances where the paths go
                            # through (string, optional)
-to <to_list>               # List of pins, instances, or clocks where the path
                            # ends (string, optional)